{"tid":490464,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[小組煞科]2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃分組賽E-H組第六輪投選專區","createTime":"2017-12-05T15:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T15:26:56.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"831d5bdb1226587bf2a5b77a83c0383d8445f2ef","tid":490464,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\nE組:<br />\n朱主愛 v 謝安琪<br />\nEmma Stone v 新垣結衣<br />\n<br />\nF組:<br />\n陳穎欣@SG v Rachel McAdams<br />\nEmma Watson v 長澤正美<br />\n<br />\nG組:<br />\nBlake Lively v Saoirse Ronan<br />\n名井南@TWICE v 唐嫣<br />\n<br />\nH組:<br />\n林明禎 v 金所炫<br />\nGal Gadot v Margot Robbie<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nE至H組第五輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kDpIVoJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkDpIVoJ.png&h=5f8968ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nE組 新垣結衣、謝安琪提早出線 Emma Stone、朱主愛篤定出局/F組 長澤正美、Emma Watson提早出線 陳穎欣@SG、Rachel McAdams篤定出局<br />\nG組 名井南@TWICE、唐嫣提早出線 Blake Lively、Saoirse Ronan篤定出局/H組 林明禎、Gal Gadot提早出線 金所炫、Margot Robbie篤定出局<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=l9ZRGHPy9kC6UW5Ma%2BxuKzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=11bf01f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b205646cdcc2ee7bdf4510ba92bb2950f239df","tid":490464,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃分組賽E組第六輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-6 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PQ0rhFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPQ0rhFq.png&h=a9a8b0ce&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zCo0EEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzCo0EEy.png&h=f2a0cb5f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mS94Fjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmS94Fjr.png&h=cd529d60&s={SIZE}\" />朱主愛 v 謝安琪<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Q6FBnk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0Q6FBnk.png&h=ded63cd8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃分組賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"83376444ab8359e6b189d0625dbe47f5135849c0","tid":490464,"uid":92376,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-12-6 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FbKHCkQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFbKHCkQ.png&h=2f038f12&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HIUU4il.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2